{"tid":2241822,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"「㤢動」其實係一種哲學思維","createTime":"2020-10-13T14:39:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-17T00:10:18.000Z","uid":274161,"like":16,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"022351e5f9a732b394106bd1d42a157352ffb1f9","tid":2241822,"uid":274161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T14:39:36.000Z","msg":"粵語有個juk1字，表示「動」，比如「周身juk1」「juk1來juk1去」「juk1手juk1腳」等<br />\n<br />\n呢個juk1字究竟點寫，大概有以下兩種意見：<br />\n逳：《廣韻&middot;入聲&middot;屋&middot;育》逳：余六切，音育。步也，轉也，行也。<br />\n㤢：《集韻》乙六切，音郁。《玉篇》心動也。<br />\n其中第二種講法被陳雄根同張錦少兩位中大教授合作編寫嘅《粵語詞匯溯源》采納。<br />\n<br />\n個人認爲，如果yuk1字寫成「㤢」，實際上反映緊佛教嘅「心動論」：<br />\n一切動作，無論外界變化定自身行爲，皆源於心動；<br />\n而呢段「心動論」，恰好又向一千三百年前（唐代）嘅廣州宣講，故而將「㤢」字當成粵語本字，都算合情合理。<br />\n<br />\n想瞭解更多，請移步 <a href=\"https://xsden.info/topic/1118/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fxsden.info%2Ftopic%2F1118%2F&d=uoj2XAvVwhv3g67ADWIJbRvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=32b13c77\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://xsden.info/topic/1118/</a><br />\n<br />\n-----------------------------<br />\n大家好，歡迎來自由匿名粵語論壇 <a href=\"http://xsden.info\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fxsden.info&d=uoj2XAvVwhv3g67ADWIJbRvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=0044e80f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">xsden.info</a> 暢所欲言！<br />\n天南地北，講乜都得，無需真實資料即可注冊！<br />\n等我哋一齊來講粵語，寫粵文，重振南粵文化！"},{"pid":"c6a23f47e79efcd8414c48c7623fbb532154fb6c","tid":2241822,"uid":60539,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T15:18:57.000Z","msg":"幾多野睇<br />\n但全部都係樓主你開既post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?"},{"pid":"ba0b5ad6a16ec0bd36566b3a06f1a83bb8eac0d1","tid":2241822,"uid":293677,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T15:28:48.000Z","msg":"不嬲用開呢個＂郁＂"},{"pid":"71c83737e9242cc610402ae14a8bc73ba868ecb6","tid":2241822,"uid":67645,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T15:48:39.000Z","msg":"幾有趣，日文就見得多佛語，樂見粵文都有得咁玩。"},{"pid":"7872c9f23676dd6c2e9dc3a3a80c43d3f9ea68b2","tid":2241822,"uid":274161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6a23f47e79efcd8414c48c7623fbb532154fb6c","tid":2241822,"uid":60539,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T15:18:57.000Z","msg":"幾多野睇<br />\n但全部都係樓主你開既post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T20:38:59.000Z","msg":"無人，有乜計 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自己又八卦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fffd6854165573e1dbaaa52a9efce86cc9654a22","tid":2241822,"uid":274161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"71c83737e9242cc610402ae14a8bc73ba868ecb6","tid":2241822,"uid":67645,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T15:48:39.000Z","msg":"幾有趣，日文就見得多佛語，樂見粵文都有得咁玩。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T20:40:43.000Z","msg":"不妨睇埋呢個po：<a href=\"https://xsden.info/topic/992/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fxsden.info%2Ftopic%2F992%2F&d=uoj2XAvVwhv3g67ADWIJbRvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=ce6fce73\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://xsden.info/topic/992/</a><br />\n「不切」其實係「不徹」，「不徹」原來係佛偈"},{"pid":"a187c082e35192a56fd176d36710de8e31189912","tid":2241822,"uid":274161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"71c83737e9242cc610402ae14a8bc73ba868ecb6","tid":2241822,"uid":67645,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T15:48:39.000Z","msg":"幾有趣，日文就見得多佛語，樂見粵文都有得咁玩。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T20:56:59.000Z","msg":"廣州當年號稱有四大叢林：光孝、六榕、華林、海幢<br />\n光孝係六祖惠能（廣東新興縣人）剃度處<br />\n達摩老祖亦從廣州登陸（細來初地，今華林寺）<br />\n照計都算一個佛門重鎮，佛學對粵語點都應該有一定影響<br />\n唔係點會有「傾佛偈」一說？"},{"pid":"a8a7b89d328026e9172b49d95cf2a63a1b4520ff","tid":2241822,"uid":274161,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a187c082e35192a56fd176d36710de8e31189912","tid":2241822,"uid":274161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"71c83737e9242cc610402ae14a8bc73ba868ecb6","tid":2241822,"uid":67645,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T15:48:39.000Z","msg":"幾有趣，日文就見得多佛語，樂見粵文都有得咁玩。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T20:56:59.000Z","msg":"廣州當年號稱有四大叢林：光孝、六榕、華林、海幢<br />\n光孝係六祖惠能（廣東新興縣人）剃度處<br />\n達摩老祖亦從廣州登陸（細來初地，今華林寺）<br />\n照計都算一個佛門重鎮，佛學對粵語點都應該有一定影響<br />\n唔係點會有「傾佛偈」一說？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T21:03:54.000Z","msg":"原來「傾偈」另一講法「謦欬」居然都同佛教有關 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<blockquote><a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/粤语\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%E7%B2%A4%E8%AF%AD&d=uoj2XAvVwhv3g67ADWIJbRvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=a564293c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/粤语</a> <br />\n謦欬一詞在古代又作謦咳，本有談笑與輕咳兩義，而後者為佛經常見用語（《妙法蓮華經&middot;如來神力品第二十一》：「一時謦欬、俱共彈指，是二音聲，遍至十方諸佛世界，地皆六種震動」；《文殊師利功德莊嚴佛土經》：「是時如來復現威德謦欬之聲。其聲遍聞十方世界」），本指欲語之前，以輕咳清喉嚨之狀，後來則引申為佛法遍傳的意思（《佛學大辭典》1922：「謦咳為將語時之狀，又為通暢之相，表本跡二門之教通暢也」），兼列為佛教「十神力」之一。僧人談佛法，民間亦說成「謦欬」。（沈德符《萬曆野獲編&middot;釋道》：「雪先下世，憨則至今神旺如盛年，乃謦欬間，多趨縉紳談時局，以是信向者愈繁。」）</blockquote>"},{"pid":"22471dbba884646b093bb26e746c93c5e971d138","tid":2241822,"uid":274161,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"ba0b5ad6a16ec0bd36566b3a06f1a83bb8eac0d1","tid":2241822,"uid":293677,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T15:28:48.000Z","msg":"不嬲用開呢個＂郁＂"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T21:05:20.000Z","msg":"你中意點寫係你自由<br />\nbut why not keep an open mind &amp; explore another possibility?"},{"pid":"c16ea29abcfe5f9ac84fb14faa82fc4ed21650e9","tid":2241822,"uid":274161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"71c83737e9242cc610402ae14a8bc73ba868ecb6","tid":2241822,"uid":67645,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T15:48:39.000Z","msg":"幾有趣，日文就見得多佛語，樂見粵文都有得咁玩。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T21:12:42.000Z","msg":"估唔到教大幾年前有人申請到funding研究<br />\n佛教及佛經翻譯對中文嘅影響<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.eduhk.hk/main/tc/research/major-projects/?id=132\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eduhk.hk%2Fmain%2Ftc%2Fresearch%2Fmajor-projects%2F%3Fid%3D132&d=uoj2XAvVwhv3g67ADWIJbRvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=0b24f377\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.eduhk.hk/main/tc/research/major-projects/?id=132</a><br />\n<br />\n孻尾有句「我們還要把目光從共同語擴大到方言，尤其是粵語的相關情形如何？」<br />\n唔知而家研究成點？"},{"pid":"0360a6939113e2ec7487f93dc1a398f606d02f82","tid":2241822,"uid":274161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"71c83737e9242cc610402ae14a8bc73ba868ecb6","tid":2241822,"uid":67645,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T15:48:39.000Z","msg":"幾有趣，日文就見得多佛語，樂見粵文都有得咁玩。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T21:14:18.000Z","msg":"日文入邊嘅佛語，不如講多幾句？"},{"pid":"a855dc0601ce1a204e1372dce0757d2e31543468","tid":2241822,"uid":274161,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"022351e5f9a732b394106bd1d42a157352ffb1f9","tid":2241822,"uid":274161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T14:39:36.000Z","msg":"粵語有個juk1字，表示「動」，比如「周身juk1」「juk1來juk1去」「juk1手juk1腳」等<br />\n<br />\n呢個juk1字究竟點寫，大概有以下兩種意見：<br />\n逳：《廣韻&middot;入聲&middot;屋&middot;育》逳：余六切，音育。步也，轉也，行也。<br />\n㤢：《集韻》乙六切，音郁。《玉篇》心動也。<br />\n其中第二種講法被陳雄根同張錦少兩位中大教授合作編寫嘅《粵語詞匯溯源》采納。<br />\n<br />\n個人認爲，如果yuk1字寫成「㤢」，實際上反映緊佛教嘅「心動論」：<br />\n一切動作，無論外界變化定自身行爲，皆源於心動；<br />\n而呢段「心動論」，恰好又向一千三百年前（唐代）嘅廣州宣講，故而將「㤢」字當成粵語本字，都算合情合理。<br />\n<br />\n想瞭解更多，請移步 <a href=\"https://xsden.info/topic/1118/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fxsden.info%2Ftopic%2F1118%2F&d=uoj2XAvVwhv3g67ADWIJbRvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=32b13c77\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://xsden.info/topic/1118/</a><br />\n<br />\n-----------------------------<br />\n大家好，歡迎來自由匿名粵語論壇 <a href=\"http://xsden.info\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fxsden.info&d=uoj2XAvVwhv3g67ADWIJbRvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=0044e80f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">xsden.info</a> 暢所欲言！<br />\n天南地北，講乜都得，無需真實資料即可注冊！<br />\n等我哋一齊來講粵語，寫粵文，重振南粵文化！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T22:30:39.000Z","msg":"段「心動論」究竟講乜？《六祖壇經》有記載<br />\n<blockquote>（慧）能後至曹溪。又被惡人尋逐。乃於四會縣避難獵人隊中。凡經一十五載。&hellip;&hellip;遂出至廣州法性寺，值印宗法師講《涅槃經》。時有風吹幡動，一僧云風動，一僧云幡動，議論不已。能進曰，不是風動，不是幡動，仁者心動。一眾駭然。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大致解釋如下：<br />\n<blockquote>相傳六祖慧能大師從師傅弘忍處接受衣砵之後，返回廣東曹溪，過了十五年，來到廣州法性寺。一晚，寺旁的旗幡被風吹動，發出颯颯的聲響，有兩位禪僧聽到，便以風和幡的幌動，作出哲理上的辯論。<br />\n<br />\n其中一個和尚說：「旗幡是被風吹動的。」譬喻自己的心本來是清淨的，只是因為有外境的紛擾而引致心動，所以外境的引動是眾禍之源。<br />\n<br />\n另一個和尚卻說：「旗幡是自己飄動的。」譬喻自己的妄心不清淨，不守本份，煩惱只不過是外緣，不是主因。所以妄心的本動性，是罪魁禍首。<br />\n<br />\n兩個人各持己見，為了風動和幡動爭論不已。六祖慧能先是冷眼旁觀，然後便插咀說：「不是風動，不是幡動，仁者心動。」</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://xsden.info/post/9568\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fxsden.info%2Fpost%2F9568&d=uoj2XAvVwhv3g67ADWIJbRvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=3352a442\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://xsden.info/post/9568</a>"},{"pid":"8a49516fd1088cdcb179ee247c2aa7c82e1452b0","tid":2241822,"uid":7427,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fffd6854165573e1dbaaa52a9efce86cc9654a22","tid":2241822,"uid":274161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"71c83737e9242cc610402ae14a8bc73ba868ecb6","tid":2241822,"uid":67645,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T15:48:39.000Z","msg":"幾有趣，日文就見得多佛語，樂見粵文都有得咁玩。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T20:40:43.000Z","msg":"不妨睇埋呢個po：<a href=\"https://xsden.info/topic/992/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fxsden.info%2Ftopic%2F992%2F&d=uoj2XAvVwhv3g67ADWIJbRvkGFRp1GVnGvdlwu1qkBE%3D&h=ce6fce73\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://xsden.info/topic/992/</a><br />\n「不切」其實係「不徹」，「不徹」原來係佛偈"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T22:39:53.000Z","msg":"留名 幾有趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dfdf9f65da918264b59734e86cfc6d12c8190c1","tid":2241822,"uid":274161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8a49516fd1088c